---
title: Peppercorn Steak with Baby Potatoes & Creamed Spinach
description: We all love a creamy peppercorn sauce. Pour it over juicy sliced steak and roast potatoes and you’ll have the ultimate dish for Valentine’s Day.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54c906c06ced6e7c1d8b4568.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/54c906c06ced6e7c1d8b4568.pdf
servings: 2
